org.afplib.afplib

Interface MMORG

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MMORGImpl

    public interface MMORG
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'MMORG'.

    The following features are supported:

    • OV Lid
    • Flags
    • OV Lname
